VALUES
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01187', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下圖為某班期中考的國文、英文、數學分數的盒形圖，關於全距（range）、中位數（median）、 四分位距（interquartilerange,IQR）、最大值、最小值，下列敘述何者正確？', '["數學的中位數最大，國文的IQR最小", "英文的全距最大，數學的IQR最小", "數學的最大值最大，英文的中位數最小", "國文的最小值最小，英文的IQR最大"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01188', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '某生物學家研究蘋果樹的枯萎病。他去一個大型蘋果園做調查，得到60%的蘋果樹開白花、 其餘的開紫花；13%的蘋果樹感染枯萎病，而且10%開紫花的蘋果樹感染枯萎病。試問，開白 花的蘋果樹感染枯萎病的機率？', '["0.04", "0.09", "0.12", "0.15"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 2, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01189', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一母體平均數為 μ，變異數為2，自母體抽取樣本 n，有關中央極限定理（Central Limit Theorem）的敘述，何者錯誤？', '["不論隨機變數X在母群體為何種分布，只要其變異數不是無限大，當樣本數夠大時，樣本 平均數x 的分布會趨近於常態分布", "樣本平均數分布的期望值 x", "樣本平均數分布的標準差 x n", "應用中央極限定理的先決條件是大樣本，所需樣本數大小與母群體分布的形狀無關"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01190', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '美國成年男性的體重分布近似於常態，平均為170磅、標準差30磅。隨機抽25位美國成年 男性，其平均體重的90%上界為下列何者？ （註：Z =1.282,Z =1.645,Z =1.960,Z =2.326）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
