  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01192', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '骨關節炎（OA）患者的肌肉功能以10分制來評估平衡協調性。隨機抽出16名OA患者，其 平均分數2.5、標準差3.0。請計算16名OA患者平均分數的95%信賴區間之寬度？ （註：Z =1.645,Z =1.960,t =1.746,t =2.120,t =1.753,t =2.131）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
