  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01194', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於檢定統計的檢定力（power），下列敘述何者正確？', '["相同條件下，資料的樣本數越大，檢定力越小", "檢定力是不拒絕一個正確的虛無假說，所以越大越好", "假設檢定的檢定力對應到診斷檢定的特異度（specificity）", "相同條件下，虛無假說與對立假說的抽樣分布重疊越少，檢定力越大"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01195', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '年齡介於65～79歲健康男性的血清尿酸的分布為近似於平均為340umol/L、標準差為80umol/L 的常態分布。由此年齡層隨機抽出4位男性，其平均血清尿酸介於260～420umol/L的機率約為 下列何者？', '["0.69", "0.73", "0.87", "0.95"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('public-health-specialist-moex-01196', 'public-health-specialist', 'public-health-specialist-moex-113-8041b019', 'sub-public-health-specialist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '某研究欲測試降血壓藥對男性、女性的效果是否相同，收集男性、女性各30位高血壓患者的 服藥前收縮壓與服藥5週後收縮壓進行分析，下列何種方法最合適？', '["單一樣本t檢定（one-samplettest）", "配對樣本t檢定（pairedttest）", "獨立樣本t檢定（independent-samplettest）", "皮爾森相關係數的t檢定（ttestforPearsoncorrelationcoefficient）"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:58+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "d5bdd3295981", "answer_pdf_sha1": "45e351b5915d", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "108", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "生物統計學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "publichealth", "db_exam_id": "public-health-specialist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
